{"tid":2237664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《國安法》下的雙十節　據報政制局設指揮中心　指示警方、食環拆「台灣旗」","createTime":"2020-10-10T12:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T04:37:19.000Z","uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ae52b3fa0b5e496682e357dec9c0f8c4789850f4","tid":2237664,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:47:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老味，驚撚到咁 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼 🇹🇼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%99%E5%8D%81%E7%AF%80-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%94%BF%E5%88%B6%E5%B1%80%E8%A8%AD%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E6%8C%87%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E6%8B%86-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%97%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259B%2599%25E5%258D%2581%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%258B%2586-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2597%2597%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDOSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=749e7d40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259B%2599%25E5%258D%2581%25E7%25AF%2580-%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258F%25AE%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%258B%2586-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2597%2597%2F&h=448f2056\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%99%E5%8D%81%E7%AF%80-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%94%BF%E5%88%B6%E5%B1%80%E8%A8%AD%E6%8C%87%E6%8F%AE%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E6%8C%87%E7%A4%BA%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E6%8B%86-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%97%97/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《蘋果日報》的報道則指，收到消息稱，政制及內地事務局要求相關部門，處理青天白日滿地紅旗的展示情況，當中食環署負責監察公眾地方，或署方管轄範圍的相關旗幟或橫額展示，若有發現須即時上報，並於 10 月 7 至 10 日，設指揮中心監督行動。行動指令特別強調，移除時要如以往般保持低調，當沒有公眾或傳媒在旁，便要立即移除，像執行日常工作般行動。<br />\n<br />\n報道亦引述局方指令，指警方會在各方巡邏，一旦發現有「台灣旗（Taiwan Flag）」便會移除，而食環職員如發現無人看顧的旗幟或橫額，情況許可下可移除。<br />\n<br />\n報道又提到，指令強調處理時要遵守 3 項原則，包括維護「一個中國」原則、依法辦事，以及針對青天白日滿地紅旗時要行動迅速，如有發現其他政治敏感物品展示亦要立刻上報。被移除的旗幟要小心處理保管，如有物主要求可發還對方。<br />\n</strong><br />\n《立場新聞》正就此向政制及內地事務局查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然面對打壓，但各區仍有市民堅持展示青天白日滿天紅旗。在將軍澳厚德邨一個單位，有戶主在窗邊掛上兩幅旗幟；創校時以「雙十」為校慶的中文大學新亞書院，據中大校園電台報道，今日書院內各處仍滿布青天白日滿地紅旗。據悉，過去兩年有市民自發到中大張貼青天白日滿地紅，校方多數不會即日移除，而會保留數天。"},{"pid":"ec2e79d481b3e1f23fdcfdf1630d7bd1a79f246d","tid":2237664,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:50:52.000Z","msg":"🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼🇹🇼"},{"pid":"fba7007dba5f27d52599889975ffc8e80f963d69","tid":2237664,"uid":183758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:52:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">共匪永遠都冇可能做正統<br />\n<br />\n慳啲啦</span>"},{"pid":"0c416ae7abe68bf5345c13c5f122db9a147a3915","tid":2237664,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no